videos.description: Brian Kelly's bunch bounced back to beat the Wolfpack handily in South Bend, Ind. ESPN college football reporter Ted Miller says a Fighting Irish weakness must hold strong to keep things rolling next week against the visiting Spartans.
videos.headline: Notre Dame overwhelms Nevada, eyes Michigan State
